data.description: Discover your dream home in Cedar City, with this exquisite twin home offering 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a spacious two-car garage. Designed with family living in mind, the property features main level living spaces and bedrooms upstairs, ensuring both comfort and privacy. The open-plan layout and modern finishes make it an ideal setting for both relaxation and entertainment.Situated in a prime location, this home places you at the heart of Cedar City's vibrant culture and close to a plethora of outdoor adventures. From top-rated schools to scenic parks and convenient shopping, everything you need is just a short drive away. Seize the opportunity to be part of a welcoming community and enjoy the best of Cedar City living.
